# libsignal build artifacts (M3.5 chunk 1A vendoring)
# Build outputs of packages/chat-crypto/scripts/build-libsignal.sh — too
# large for git (~337MB iOS xcframework + ~159MB Android AAR). Contributors
# run the script after clone; future CI fetches prebuilt release assets.
# Binary checksums skipped too — non-reproducible across build machines
# (embedded timestamps + paths). The SOURCE-tree manifest LibSignalClient.sha256
# is committed because it is reproducible.
packages/chat-crypto/ios/SignalFfi.xcframework/
packages/chat-crypto/ios/SignalFfi.xcframework.sha256
packages/chat-crypto/android/libs/*.aar
packages/chat-crypto/android/libs/*.aar.sha256
packages/chat-mls-core/ios/chat_mls_coreFFI.xcframework/**/chat_mls_coreFFI